The series also keeps tabs on the efforts of teenager Parker Schnabel and old-timer Dakota Fred to hit the mother lode at separate sites.

programme.title: Life in the Great Wetlands
programme.desc: The flooded zones of the Loango National Park in Gabon form an extraordinary mosaic and a complex of deeply interconnected biotopes. programme.title: Life in the Great Wetlands
programme.desc: Documentary series looking at the remarkable biodiversity found in wetland regions. In the Sabah region of East Malaysia lies one of the island of Borneos last wildlife strongholds. programme.title: Life in the Great Wetlands
programme.desc: Documentary series looking at the remarkable biodiversity found in wetland regions. programme.title: Life in the Great Wetlands
